### Resolution
_There is currently no code example available on how to remedy error 11030. Please modify the code below in a way that can describe how to remedy this error._

```csharp
using Starcounter;
using System;

class Program {
    static void Main(string[] args) {
        // We call PreFoo() prior to calling Foo(). Now, we will
        // no longer experience error 11030.
        Db.PreFoo();
        Db.Foo();
    }
}
```
